                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.85/176: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-05-27T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 27, 1943—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>554. Department’s 531, May 20, 6 p.m. The War Shipping Administration, under date
                    of May 20 submitted to Mr. Subercaseaux an offer for the three vessels. There
                    has been no response as yet from Subercaseaux.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
